reviewText:
Many famous celebrities, a lot of fun to watch wish it was on DVD.
William Brooks - Toronto

More than 10 years ago I borrowed this tape from library.  My daughter was very enjoying, over and over she was watched this movie( she is multi disable, she was 9 year-old), and I made copy for her, but after many years that tape condition is getting rough, I was looking for this movie long time. I wanted her to have good time again, so and now she is enjoying again.
My daughter has been looking for this for years. I live in fear of our tape breaking. Its a very fun video and definatly worthy of an upgrade. Hop to it!
